&lt;li&gt;Published research or practical experience in scientific AI applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with modern machine learning techniques and model training methodologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with biological databases (UniProt, GenBank, PDB) and computational biology tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
